***List of abbreviations (H.Asano) ***

ST1 = Drift chamber (Tracker for Scattered particle)
IT1 = Internal Drift chamber 
BSFT = Scintilating Fiber Tracker for beam particle
SSFT = Scintilating Fiber Tracker for scattered particle
Hodo = HodoScope
RHC = RawHitContainer
ITOF = Internal TOF -> RPC or TOP ?
PID1 & 2 = Thereshold type Aerogel cherenkov or TOP
PID1 downstream
PID2 upstream
AFT = Assist Fiber Tracker (Fiber Wall)
MF = Muon Filter
VD = Virtual Detector

***code explanation***

PreIn Tracking = tracking which requires S_SFT and Internal TOF
PreOut Tracking = tracking which requires DC1 and DC2

actual implementation TrAnalyzer.cc



There is no beam-RICH at this moment (Sep.20th, 2016)


